106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/carsten-brzeski/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Carsten Brzeski</a></em></p> <p></p> <h2>The ECB drops a key policy line</h2> <p>The ECB cut interest rates by 25bp, bringing the deposit rate to 3%, its lowest level since March 2023. This decision reflects a compromise between growth and inflation worriers, a gut</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743934-another-rate-cut-from-ecb-next-stop-is-neutral", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 20:10:00"}, {"id": "4743915", "title": "SPMC: New CLO Equity CEF Raises Monthly Dividend Again, Now Yields 13%", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2058537479/image_2058537479.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Only 1 of 5 ladders reach in ascending order\" data-id=\"2058537479\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1122px\" srcset=\"h