gure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young couple swimming in cave filming on camera\" data-id=\"1444443512\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Topline Summary</h2> <p>Kyverna Therapeutics, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KYTX\" title=\"Kyverna Therapeutics, Inc.\">KYTX</a></span>) is one of several contenders to a heretofore unclaimed crown: engineered cell therapy for the treatment of inflammatory disorders. This has been a dovetailing effort with the chimeric antigen</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1444443512/image_1444443512.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743849-kyverna-therapeutics-car-t-cells-trying-to-impact-inflammatory-disorders", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 20:00:00"}, {"id": "4743930", "title": "Liquidity Services, Inc. 2024 Q4 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Liquidity Services, Inc. in conjunction with their 2024 Q4 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106144\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743930-liquidity-services-inc-2024-q4-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 19:51:06"}, {"id": "4743926", "title": "When Tariffs Hit: Stocks, Bonds, And Volatility", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Currency and Exchange Stock Chart for Finance and Economy Display\" data-id=\"1358927461\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cemagraphics</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It\u2019s been only a little more than a month since the US Presidential election, and already analysts\u2019 heads are spinning over the potential impact of trade policy. President-elect Trump has made numerous tariff threats, leaving researchers to wonder which, if any, he\u2019ll follow through</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743926-when-tariffs-hit-stocks-bonds-and-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 19:50:00"}, {"id": "4743914", "title": "Serve Robotics: Let The Robots Cool Off", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149992351/image_2149992351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Futuristic city with autonomous delivery mini vans on the road\" data-id=\"2149992351\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149992351/image_2149992351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149992351/image_2149992351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149992351/image_2149992351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149992351/image_2149992351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/21